Adapter

Adapter pattern helps to combine two incompatible interfaces.

IMPLEMENTATION

Interfaces:

1. Player::Media
2. Player::AdvancedMedia

Concrete classes implementing interface Player::AdvancedMedia:

1. Player::AdvancedMedia::VLC
2. Player::AdvancedMedia::MP4

Concrete classes implementing interface Player::Media:

1. Player::Media::Adapter
2. Player::Media::Audio
